  "detailed_description": "If you love colours, you'll love Spectrum: a relaxing colour sorting game in three dimensions which tests your skill in matching tints, shades, value and hue.<br><br>The Challenge: to re-assemble the cube, putting each block in its place between the corners. You'll never play the same cube twice!<br><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Infinite levels<br></li><li> Tools: Build Frame, Pop, Scooch<br></li><li> Save progress<br></li><li> Eject any misplaced blocks<br></li><li> Search through the floating blocks with vortex<br></li><li> Mistakes can be easy to find with an outline option</li></ul><br>Compatible with Razer Chroma keyboards. VR gameplay coming soon<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743220/extras/20a27db9baa1bd0b1aeb33149bcb33ff.poster.avif?t=1648176233\" width=630 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743220/extras/20a27db9baa1bd0b1aeb33149bcb33ff.webm?t=1648176233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743220/extras/20a27db9baa1bd0b1aeb33149bcb33ff.mp4?t=1648176233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743220/extras/72eea9aa3df5b871b1c415db357808df.poster.avif?t=1648176233\" width=246 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743220/extras/72eea9aa3df5b871b1c415db357808df.webm?t=1648176233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743220/extras/72eea9aa3df5b871b1c415db357808df.mp4?t=1648176233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_im